snippet.title: Super Alloy Crush   Teaser Trailer   EN
snippet.description:
Steam :https://store.steampowered.com/app/3092360/_/

"Super Alloy Crush" is a 2D side-scrolling fighting action game. Play as Kelly and Muu (No.02) to defeat enemies and obtain treasure! Join hands with friends and take on challenges together!

Wishlist the game on Steam!
